  Locus:
    Page: 243
    Verse: 3
Tags:
  - Heaven & Hell
---
Earth cannot escape heaven. Flee it by going up, or flee it by going down,
heaven still invades earth, energizes it, makes it sacred. All hiding
places reveal God. If you want to escape God, He runs in your lap. For God
is at home. It is we who have gone out for a walk.
